import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'
import vuetify from './plugins/vuetify'
import './plugins/axios'

Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  router,
  vuetify,
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app') 

// 在 src/main.js 中添加
document.title = 'Andy Casket Services' // 修改网页标题
document.querySelector('link[rel="icon"]').href = '/favicon.ico' // 修改网页图标
